name: DogeKing Metaverse
description:
DogeKing Metaverse is the extension, next part of Dogeking project, which has done tremendously well. We are trending in the whole of China, have been promoted by one of the biggest Chinese comedians, and more than 1 billion people have heard our name from the Chuwan Chinese New Year Met Gala show.

Join us on our journey, where we will introduce our DogeKing in to his very own metaverse, consisting of many worlds, where users are able to play, adopt, trade and create their very own worlds. Our full website will be launched very soon, along with our game. Keep tuned.
